WEBVTT

00:02.713 --> 00:06.175
On Friday, Yahoo! announced that the company is up for sale.

00:06.681 --> 00:09.785
Yahoo! has hired a strategic team of lawyers and bankers...

00:09.867 --> 00:11.628
....to begin exploring alternatives.

00:12.027 --> 00:16.001
The announcement comes at a time when Yahoo! has been making huge amounts of layoffs,...

00:16.305 --> 00:18.643
...cutting nearly 15% of its workforce.

00:19.055 --> 00:22.977
Yahoo! is still a popular Web destination with its news-focused home page...

00:23.366 --> 00:26.681
...but it continues to struggle with its core web advertising business.

00:27.121 --> 00:30.885
In a recent press release, Yahoo! CEO Marissa Mayer stated,...

00:31.217 --> 00:34.603
..."As both shareholders and employees, all of us here at Yahoo!...

00:34.685 --> 00:37.582
...want to return this iconic company to greatness."

